<div class="return max-w-4xl mx-auto py-12 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="text-center mb-12">
    <h1 class="font-bold text-5xl md:text-6xl mb-4">Return & Refund Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      At Echo It, we want you to be completely satisfied with your purchase. If for any reason you are not satisfied, we have a simple and straightforward return and refund policy to ensure your peace of mind.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- Return Process -->
  <section class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="font-semibold text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-4">How to Return an Item</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      We accept returns for items in new and unused condition. If you would like to return an item, please follow the steps below:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-decimal list-inside pl-4">
      <li>Contact us within 14 days of receiving your order.</li>
      <li>Provide your order number and the reason for the return.</li>
      <li>Ship the item back to us in its original packaging.</li>
      <li>Once we receive the returned item, we will process your refund within 7 business days.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <!-- Return Conditions -->
  <section class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="font-semibold text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-4">Return Conditions</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      To ensure that your return is processed smoothly, please adhere to the following conditions:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-decimal list-inside pl-4">
      <li>The item must be in its original condition and packaging.</li>
      <li>Items must be returned within 14 days of receiving the order.</li>
      <li>Return shipping costs are the responsibility of the customer unless the item is defective or damaged upon arrival.</li>
      <li>Personalized or custom items cannot be returned unless defective.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <!-- Refund Policy -->
  <section class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="font-semibold text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-4">Refund Policy</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      Once your return is processed, we will issue a refund to the original payment method. Please allow up to 7 business days for the refund to appear in your account. If you paid via credit card, the processing time may vary depending on your card issuer.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- Exchanges -->
  <section class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="font-semibold text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-4">Exchanges</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      If you would like to exchange an item, we recommend following the return process first and then placing a new order for the desired item. Unfortunately, we do not process direct exchanges.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact Us -->
  <section class="text-center">
    <h2 class="font-semibold text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-4">Need Help?</h2>
    <p class="mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      If you have any questions about our return policy, please donâ€™t hesitate to contact us. Our customer service team is here to assist you.
    </p>
    <%# link_to 'Contact Us', contact_path, class: 'btn btn-primary' %>
  </section>
</div>
